OL,3,CHeadteacher jailed after attacking his
OL,4,Cdeputy due to "sexual jealousy"
OL,6,FFelton paced behind Pyke, whilst he
OL,7,Fsat in a chair, before producing the
OL,8,Fweapon and striking him multiple times
OL,9,Fin the head.
OL,11,FMr Pyke fell to the ground and
OL,12,Fattempted to kick away his attacker,
OL,13,Fbefore colleagues at the school in
OL,14,FAberavon, south Wales, heard the
OL,15,Fdisturbance and called the emergency
OL,16,Fservices to assist.
OL,18,FIeuan Rees, for the prosecution, said
OL,19,FFelton believed Mr Pyke had slept with
OL,20,Fanother teacher with whom he had
OL,21,Frecently been in a relationship.
