OL,3,CHeadteacher jailed after attacking his
OL,4,Cdeputy due to "sexual jealousy"
OL,6,F"The evidence of his wife and the
OL,7,Fadmissions he made to her suggested Mr
OL,8,FFelton had been in a relationship with
OL,9,Fanother member of staff and had
OL,10,Frecently discovered he was the father
OL,11,Fof her child," he said.
OL,13,F"Furthermore, he believed that Mr Pyke
OL,14,Fhad now begun his own relationship
OL,15,Fwith that lady."
OL,17,FFollowing the incident on 5th March
OL,18,Fthis year, Felton threw the wrench
OL,19,Faway and left the school in his car.
