OL,3,CHeadteacher jailed after attacking his
OL,4,Cdeputy due to "sexual jealousy"
OL,6,FHe then sent an email to all staff
OL,7,Fapologising "for the problems and
OL,8,Fdistress his actions were likely to
OL,9,Fcause".
OL,11,FAccording to an annual report, he was
OL,12,Fappointed as headteacher in September
OL,13,F2023.
OL,15,FJudge Paul Thomas KC sentenced him at
OL,16,FSwansea Crown Court on Friday to two
OL,17,Fyears and four months in jail.
OL,19,FHe was also given a restraining order.
