OL,3,CHeadteacher jailed after attacking his
OL,4,Cdeputy due to "sexual jealousy"
OL,6,F"The level of unprovoked violence,
OL,7,Ffrom a professional in the workplace,
OL,8,Fwas shocking.
OL,10,F"Too often we see attacks of this
OL,11,Fnature result in life changing
OL,12,Finjuries or fatal consequences, and
OL,13,Fthankfully, that was not the result in
OL,14,Fthis case."
