OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Simon Davies of
OL,7,FSouth Wales Police said: "Anthony
OL,8,FFelton's actions have resulted in him
OL,9,Fgoing to prison, have had a
OL,10,Fsignificant impact on his personal
OL,11,Flife and have destroyed his decades-
OL,12,Flong teaching career ` not to mention
OL,13,Fthe physical impact upon the victim,
OL,14,Fwho we are pleased is on the road to
OL,15,Frecovery.
